  "texts": [
    "They effectively moved away from the nest and searched a wider area, increasing their chances of encountering food sources more quickly and efficiently.",
    "To enhance the randomness of the ants' exploration, we expanded their rotation options to include \"random.\"",
    "This meant that when the LLM selected \"random\" as the rotation action, it was making a high-level decision to delegate the choice of direction to chance.",
    "In the simulation, this \"random' ' option was implemented at a programming level in NetLogo to randomly choose the direction of rotation either left or right.",
    "Through iterative tuning, we significantly enhanced the simulated ants' behavior, making it more consistent with the ant foraging dynamics observed in the rule-based NetLogo model."
